flowchart TD
    A[Human Intent] --> B[Intent Translator]
    B --> C[Mission Contract]
    C --> D[Orchestrator]
    D --> E[Implementation Agent]
    E --> F[Evidence + Owned Outputs]
    F --> G[Critic / Reviewer]
    G --> H{Evidence Judge}
    H -->|Pass| I[User-facing Result]
    H -->|Missing Evidence| D
    H -->|Wrong Boundary| J[Local or Privileged Execution]
    J --> F
